text: Nizhneakbashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Sharipovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 184 as of 2010. There are 13 streets. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Kushnarenkovo, 1 km from Sharipovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Nizhneakbashevo
